524
00:57:13,139 --> 00:57:14,723
<i>and the lines were easy to memorize.</i>

525
00:57:17,059 --> 00:57:19,228
<i>I was worried a bit</i>
<i>because the theater was old.</i>

526
00:57:21,313 --> 00:57:22,690
