ROOM 5
CHA WOO-SIK

529
00:57:28,404 --> 00:57:30,489
(CHIEF MOURNER) PARK SE-YEONG
(CHILD) CHA DONG-WON

530
00:57:30,573 --> 00:57:34,952
<i>It would've been nice if I had gotten out</i>
<i>after the last audience did…</i>

531
